Titolo: Cryptark

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Cryptark is an action roguelike video game developed and published by Alientrap for Microsoft Windows, OS X, Linux, and PlayStation 4. The game was released on Microsoft Windows and PlayStation 4 on June 20, 2017.
A sequel named Gunhead is currently in development by Alientrap, and set for release in 2022. Unlike its predecessor, Gunhead will be played from a first-person perspective with VR implementation being a post-release possibility.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: 77
